# Cryochamber runtime (per-machine state). The chamber *design* — .cryo/plan.md,
# .cryo/cryo.toml, .cryo/README.md — is committed; everything below is local.
# Advisor drafts under .zulip/.drafts/ are already covered by the .zulip/ rule.
.cryo/NOTES.md
.cryo/messages/
.cryo/*.log
.cryo/timer.json
.cryo/todo.json
.cryo/.cryo/
.cryo/tmp/
